.appledaily.com/local/20210310/P363FSO6YFAJFFM6IJQAQSL6EM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FP363FSO6YFAJFFM6IJQAQSL6EM%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=beefda3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FP363FSO6YFAJFFM6IJQAQSL6EM%2F&h=7010e989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/P363FSO6YFAJFFM6IJQAQSL6EM/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:11:01.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;忠誠嘅廢物&rdquo;要bye bye <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4664affe914a9135c4067aafa3f6f7963f4d0fb","tid":2440160,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gpu8Lsf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgpu8Lsf.jpg&h=7336000a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9b109a41efd0af77c860a06b452749fdb072da5","tid":2440160,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:13:06.000Z","msg":"撚人就有<br />\n能人投外<br />\n出賣中共"},{"pid":"3690e2cb9d163d5a0e0b76395649cf066e0478b5","tid":2440160,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:15:02.000Z","msg":"好難啦<br />\n<br />\n仆你個街<br />\n文革六四鬥死哂人<br />\n有幾多人材呀大陸<br />\n<br />\n至於香港<br />\n你要搵個智力正常但唔好咁講野摟打既處理香港事務<br />\n有咩大鑊野叫兩隻傻仔kol 做大龍鳳約隻揪<br />\n咪平平安安囉<br />\n<br />\n我利申留港準備被強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439390f6960f70804e16633c677f3074e5c2f4b0","tid":2440160,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:16:01.000Z","msg":"成班為咗著數都只會講佢想聽嘅嘢，點會有有能之士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19198b0b37947f780ffc17e79b4c97452cba8b1e","tid":2440160,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be580dda9d209eaacf785ecdaef90e8ef70bc738","tid":2440160,"uid":387907,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:00:29.000Z","msg":"你中共唔搞鳩香港<br />\n啲人咪愛國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n停150人<br />\n唔好迫香港用埋啲垃圾<br />\n唔好唯我獨尊咁高高在上<br />\n所有香港政策以港人為先<br />\n停止嗰啲政治任務<br />\n<br />\n大家快快樂樂做隻港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嘅建議<br />\n1. 拉晒嗰班白衫人<br />\n2. 重組警隊，清晒啲犯罪者<br />\n3. 終止嗰條黨安法，放晒香港啲政治犯<br />\n4. 放低你嘅死人面子，大時大節例如農曆新年用廣東話話返句恭喜發財<br />\n5. 遵守返承諾，河水不犯井水，唔好再迫香港做啲咩政治任務（嗰啲咩國民教育、23條、逃犯條例唔好再搞喇）<br />\n6. 遵守承諾，畀返個無限制嘅真普選香港人。你荒選出嚟嗰個真係會敢走去獨立，或者天滅中共咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7. 70/80年代英國佬做咗啲乜去令香港人安心，照返做咪得囉<br />\n8. 國家無錢咪出聲囉，唔好懶大方咁，喺基本法上面寫話軍費由中央負責，轉個頭又整個咩國安部要香港一年畀幾千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做好自己就自然大把人跟隨啦戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:18:10.000Z","msg":"智者"},{"pid":"0295469147ef5a88ae627892fcce7cb60bb4b554","tid":2440160,"uid":53515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSV0BB7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSV0BB7.jpg&h=e8dcbee8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"37309264e2c301d3a6d86911103990d53799bdcd","tid":2440160,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"原來香港人慘到只係奢求有瓦遮頭<br />\n又loop房屋問題就知解決唔到問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1150fd6c5bbf9ccac3b8947c43b676d22ff9c0ea","tid":2440160,"uid":202511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18577e9d238815156554ab5af3315ce9f77b790e","tid":2440160,"uid":363016,"like":4,"dislike":0